{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Anyone guilty of killing an emergency services worker to be jailed for life",
        "additional_details": "We ask emergency services workers to keep the peace. To save lives. To protect us.\r\n\r\nSo society must offer the greatest protection for those killed protecting it.\r\n\r\nThat is what Harper\u2019s Law will provide - an appropriate deterrent and a suitable punishment.",
        "background": "We are calling for #HarpersLaw. \r\n\r\nThe creation of this law -  spearheaded by Lissie Harper, the widow of hero PC Andrew Harper - would mean anyone found guilty of killing a police officer, firefighter, nurse, doctor, prison officer or paramedic would be jailed for life.",
